SIMPLE: mandatory
RECORDS: 2

==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mandatory
<hw>Man"da*to*ry</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>mandatorius</ets>.]</ety> <sn>1.</sn> <def>Containing a command;
preceptive; directory.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Obligatory; compulsory; required by
authority.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <fld>(Law)</fld> <def>Not optional; not able to be
modified or disregarded; <as>as, seven <ex>mandatory</ex> clauses in the
contract</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>PJC</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mandatory</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Mandatory
<hw>Man"da*to*ry</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>Same as
<er>Mandatary</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mandelate</ent>⟦br⟧
